  "description" : "* Based on a history adventure manga by http://anidb.net/cr8467 [Matsui Yuusei].\nIn medieval Japan, eight-year-old http://anidb.net/ch131367 [Houjou Tokiyuki] is the heir to the Kamakura shogunate. But the Houjou clan is in decline, and Tokiyuki`s peaceful days of playing hide-and-seek with his teachers come to an abrupt end when his clan is betrayed from within. The lone survivor of his family, Tokiyuki is the rightful heir to the throne, but to take it back, he`ll have to do what he does best—run away!\nSource: Viz\nNote: The first episode received an early screening at a special event on June 23, 2024 at Tsurugaoka Hachimanguu in Kamakura and on July 2, 2024 at Shinjuku Wald 9 in Tokyo. The regular TV broadcast started on July 6, 2024.",
